# Lock files for v3 parallel-track coordination.
#
# Per admin/SHIP_STANDARDIZATION_PLAN_V3.md § 11, agents working a fleet line
# write a JSON lock here before editing ships/<line>/*.html. The pre-commit
# hook rejects commits that touch a line currently locked by a different
# branch.
#
# Lock filename:  <line>.lock        (e.g. rcl.lock, carnival.lock)
# Lock contents:  { "branch": "...", "agent": "...", "started_at": "...", "ttl_minutes": 720 }
#
# Stale locks (older than ttl_minutes) are reaped by the pre-commit hook.
